  <description type="morphology">Plants (0.3–)0.5–1.5 × (0.1–)0.3–1.5 dm. Leaves: petiole (3–)10–20 mm; proximal blades 2–5(–6) × 2–5(–7) mm, acerose, distal blades 3–5 × 0.5–1.5 mm, awn-tipped. Involucral bracts 2–5 mm; awns 1–3 mm. Flowers 0.8–1 mm. Achenes 1–1.2 mm.</description>
